# ==========================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ==========================================
# This .gitignore is designed to prevent accidental
# commits of sensitive information. Always review
# your commits before pushing to ensure no secrets
# are included.
#
# Remember to:
# 1. Never commit API keys, tokens, or passwords
# 2. Use environment variables for sensitive config
# 3. Regularly audit your repository for leaked secrets
# 4. Use tools like git-secrets for additional protection
#
# For more security best practices, see:
# https://github.com/VanZoel112/vzoelv2/blob/main/SECURITY.md